    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207229</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">The Diaries of George Washington</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Tagebücher von George Washington</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les agendas de George Washington</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os diários de George Washington</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I diari di George Washington</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τα ημερολόγια George Ουάσιγκτον</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Los diarios de George Washington</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">features the colorful diaries of the first U.S. President, written between 1748 and 1799. They chronicle his life from his time as a self-made farmer to his tenure as a soldier-statesman.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">kennzeichnet die bunten Tagebücher des ersten 
VEREINIGTE STAATEN Präsidenten, geschrieben zwischen 1748 und 1799. 
Sie zeichnen seine Lebensdauer von seiner Zeit als 
Selbst-gebildeter Landwirt zu seinem Besitz als Soldat-Staatsmann auf.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">comporte les agendas colorés du premier 
président des ETATS-UNIS, écrits entre 1748 et 1799. Ils font 
la chronique de sa vie de son temps en tant que fermier de 
art de l'auto-portrait-made à sa tenure comme soldier-homme d'État.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">caracteriza os diários coloridos do primeiro 
presidente de ESTADOS UNIDOS, escritos entre 1748 e 1799. 
Chronicle sua vida de seu tempo como um fazendeiro self-feito a 
seu tenure como um soldado-soldier-statesman.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">caratterizza i diari colorful del primo presidente
degli STATI UNITI, scritti fra 1748 e 1799. Chronicle la sua 
vita dal suo tempo come coltivatore auto-fatto al suo possesso come 
soldier-statista.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">χαρακτηρίζει τα ζωηρόχρωμα ημερολόγια του πρώτου 
ΑΜΕΡΙΚΑΝΙΚΟΥ Προέδρου, που γράφονται μεταξύ 1748 και 1799. 
Εξιστορούν κατά γράμμα τη ζωή του από το χρόνο του ως 
μόνος-γίνοντα αγρότη στη διάρκεια αξιώματός του ως 
στρατιώτης-πολιτικό.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">ofrece los diarios coloridos del primer presidente
de ESTADOS UNIDOS, escritos entre 1748 y 1799. Chronicle su vida
a partir de su tiempo como granjero uno mismo-hecho a su arrendamiento
como soldado-estadista.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
